<subSubSection id="EFC65CDDFF9ABE1FFF7BFBA6FE08F01A" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="A7630F56FF9ABE1FFF7BFBA6FE08F01A" blockId="34.[151,1127,1072,1319]" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">
<emphasis id="95A8D344FF9ABE1FFF7BFBA6FEF8F15A" bold="true" box="[151,262,1072,1095]" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">Remarks.</emphasis>
After the description of 
<taxonomicName id="60DC74D5FF9ABE1FFDF5FBA6FD8AF15A" authorityName="Miessen &amp; Trichas" authorityYear="2011" box="[537,628,1072,1095]" class="Insecta" family="Bolboceratidae" genus="Bolbelasmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="keithi">
<emphasis id="95A8D344FF9ABE1FFDF5FBA6FD8AF15A" box="[537,628,1072,1095]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">B. keithi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion id="6518C1B4FF9ABE1FFD57FBA6FD0BF15A" box="[699,757,1072,1095]" country="Greece" name="Kriti" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">Crete</collectingRegion>
and Kasos Islands by 
<bibRefCitation id="C34D72A7FF9ABE1FFC1DFBA6FEC2F17A" author="MIESSEN &amp; TRICHAS" firstAuthor="MIESSEN" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" pagination="182 - 188" refId="ref27744" refString="MIESSEN G. &amp; TRICHAS A. 2011: Description d'un nouveau Bolbelasmus Boucomont, 1911 du sud de l'Archipel Egeen (Coleoptera, Scarabaeoidea, Bolboceratidae). Lambillionea 111: 182 - 188." type="journal article" year="2011">MIESSEN &amp; TRICHAS (2011)</bibRefCitation>
, the record of 
<taxonomicName id="60DC74D5FF9ABE1FFE35FBC6FDA2F17A" baseAuthorityName="Schrank von Paula" baseAuthorityYear="1789" box="[473,604,1104,1127]" class="Insecta" family="Bolboceratidae" genus="Bolbelasmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="unicornis">
<emphasis id="95A8D344FF9ABE1FFE35FBC6FDA2F17A" box="[473,604,1104,1127]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">B. unicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Rhodes by 
<bibRefCitation id="C34D72A7FF9ABE1FFCF5FBC6FC17F17A" author="SCHATZMAYR" box="[793,1001,1104,1127]" firstAuthor="SCHATZMAYR" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" pagination="9 - 23" refId="ref28467" refString="SCHATZMAYR A. 1936: Risultati scientifici delle cacce entomologiche di S. A. S. il principe Alessandro Della Torre e Tasso nelle isole dell'Egeo. VI. Scarabaeidae. Bollettino Laboratorio Zoologia Generale Agraria Reale Istituto Superiore Agrario Portici 30: 9 - 23." type="journal article" year="1936">SCHATZMAYR (1936)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="C34D72A7FF9ABE1FFBF2FBC6FF21F19A" author="MIKSIC" firstAuthor="MIKSIC" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" pagination="47 - 136" refId="ref27780" refString="MIKSIC R. 1959: Dritter Nachtrag zur &quot; Fauna Insectorum Balcanica-Scarabaeidae &quot;. Godisnjak Bioloskog Instituta Univerziteta u Sarajevu 12: 47 - 136." type="journal article" year="1959">MIKŠIĆ (1959)</bibRefCitation>
needed to be confirmed. Actually, following 
<bibRefCitation id="C34D72A7FF9ABE1FFD55FBE6FC2DF19A" author="MIESSEN &amp; TRICHAS" box="[697,979,1136,1159]" firstAuthor="MIESSEN" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" pagination="182 - 188" refId="ref27744" refString="MIESSEN G. &amp; TRICHAS A. 2011: Description d'un nouveau Bolbelasmus Boucomont, 1911 du sud de l'Archipel Egeen (Coleoptera, Scarabaeoidea, Bolboceratidae). Lambillionea 111: 182 - 188." type="journal article" year="2011">MIESSEN &amp; TRICHAS (2011)</bibRefCitation>
, we identified the Rhodes specimens as 
<taxonomicName id="60DC74D5FF9ABE1FFE47FB06FDFBF1BA" authorityName="Miessen &amp; Trichas" authorityYear="2011" box="[427,517,1168,1191]" class="Insecta" family="Bolboceratidae" genus="Bolbelasmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="keithi">
<emphasis id="95A8D344FF9ABE1FFE47FB06FDFBF1BA" box="[427,517,1168,1191]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">B. keithi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, thus definitively excluding the presence of 
<taxonomicName id="60DC74D5FF9ABE1FFC0FFB06FB99F1BA" baseAuthorityName="Schrank von Paula" baseAuthorityYear="1789" box="[995,1127,1168,1191]" class="Insecta" family="Bolboceratidae" genus="Bolbelasmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="unicornis">
<emphasis id="95A8D344FF9ABE1FFC0FFB06FB99F1BA" box="[995,1127,1168,1191]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">B. unicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the Mediterranean islands (see also 
<bibRefCitation id="C34D72A7FF9ABE1FFDD1FB26FCBEF1DA" author="ARNONE &amp; MASSA" box="[573,832,1200,1223]" firstAuthor="ARNONE" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" pagination="401 - 414" refId="ref26188" refString="ARNONE M. &amp; MASSA B. 2010: A new species of Bolbelasmus Boucomont, 1911 from Sicily (Italy). Il Naturalista Siciliano 34: 401 - 414." type="journal article" year="2010">ARNONE &amp; MASSA 2010</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="C34D72A7FF9ABE1FFCA1FB26FC1AF1DA" author="MIESSEN G." box="[845,996,1200,1223]" journalOrPublisher="Lambillionea" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" pagination="109 - 119" part="111" refId="ref27715" refString="MIESSEN G. 2011: Quelques commentaires sur le genre Bolbelasmus Boucomont, 1911 et description d'une nouvelle espece de Chypre. Lambillionea 111: 109 - 119." title="Quelques commentaires sur le genre Bolbelasmus Boucomont, 1911 et description d'une nouvelle espece de Chypre" type="journal article" year="2011">MIESSEN 2011</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="C34D72A7FF9ABE1FFC1EFB26FED0F1FA" author="MIESSEN &amp; TRICHAS" firstAuthor="MIESSEN" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" pagination="182 - 188" refId="ref27744" refString="MIESSEN G. &amp; TRICHAS A. 2011: Description d'un nouveau Bolbelasmus Boucomont, 1911 du sud de l'Archipel Egeen (Coleoptera, Scarabaeoidea, Bolboceratidae). Lambillionea 111: 182 - 188." type="journal article" year="2011">MIESSEN &amp; TRICHAS 2011</bibRefCitation>
). Therefore the above mentioned specimens constitute the first record of 
<taxonomicName id="60DC74D5FF9ABE1FFBA3FB46FF2CF01A" authorityName="Miessen &amp; Trichas" authorityYear="2011" class="Insecta" family="Bolboceratidae" genus="Bolbelasmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="245" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="keithi">
<emphasis id="95A8D344FF9ABE1FFBA3FB46FF2CF01A" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="245">B. keithi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the island of Rhodes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
